Package: multiGGM
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Inference of Multiple Gaussian Graphical Models
Version: 0.0.3
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Christine B.", family = "Peterson", role = c("aut")),
    person(given = "First", family = "Last", role = c("cre"), email = "first.last@example.com"))
Description: Utilities and MCMC implementation for Bayesian inference of multiple
    Gaussian graphical models as in Peterson, Stingo, and Vannucci (2015, JASA).
    Includes a high-performance implementation of the Markov random field (MRF)
    normalizing constant used for edge-sharing priors, plus parallel multi-chain
    orchestration and helpers to convert precision matrices to partial correlations.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
